+ * rough estimate of a rolling average with ~ time constant of 32ms.
+ * 80/128 ~ 0.63. * 80 / 32768 / 128 == * 5 / 262144
+ * Make sure a call to update_clocks has been made before calling this to get
+ * an updated rq->niffies.
